4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper does not directly deal with social networks, but the optimization of compressed sensing measurements over noisy channels can be applied to networked systems. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper does not directly deal with computer vision, but the optimization of compressed sensing measurements can be applied to image and video compression.
